# Force LF (Linux) line endings for shell scripts (.sh)
# Reason:
# - Bash scripts fail on Linux/WSL when checked out with CRLF line endings (\r\n)
# - This repo is used across Windows, WSL, and Linux
# - Enforcing LF prevents runtime errors like:
#      $'\r': command not fout
#
# Please do NOT change this unless you know exactly why.

*sh text eol=lf